and it's driving me crazy.

01:42.575 --> 01:43.774
Everywhere I look,
I see her.

01:43.776 --> 01:45.192
I see her walking on the street;

01:45.194 --> 01:47.811
I see her shopping in the store;

01:47.813 --> 01:49.830
I see her dancing on that pole.

01:49.832 --> 01:51.915
I see her dancing
on that pole, too.

01:51.917 --> 01:54.251
Oh, my God, that's Quinn.

01:54.253 --> 01:57.437
